data.title: Excellent Music Wiki:Article Requests
data.text:
This is a page where only admins and mods can add request articles for good music, good artists, and iconic moments in music history. To admins and mods; please insert them in the list below. It is recommended that you remove them once they have been added. Note that the forbidden pages are not to be added. If you would like to request a song, album, moment, or singer to be added onto this list, ask any of our admins and mods.
